org.safs.autoit

Class AutoItRs.DefaultRecognizable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.persist.PersistableDefault
      • org.safs.autoit.AutoItRs.DefaultRecognizable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoItRs.Recognizable, Persistable, Printable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AutoItRs.DefaultRecognizableAutoIt
    Enclosing class:
    AutoItRs

    protected static class AutoItRs.DefaultRecognizable
extends PersistableDefault
implements AutoItRs.Recognizable
    This class provides default implementation of interface AutoItRs.Recognizable.
    As the field of name starting with Constants.AutoItConstants.PREFIX_PROPERTY_FOR_RS will be used for generating recognition string, please avoid adding new fields of name starting with Constants.AutoItConstants.PREFIX_PROPERTY_FOR_RS to this class when refactoring this class.
